{"image_id": "PHM_2013_page_73", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "PULTEGROUP, INC.", "bbox": [521.6, 33.8, 716.3, 56.9]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS (continued)", "bbox": [293.0, 58.8, 944.8, 81.9]}, {"text": "69", "bbox": [608.6, 1549.2, 629.4, 1572.2]}, {"text": "9.  Stock compensation plans", "bbox": [85.5, 114.0, 342.0, 137.1]}, {"text": "We maintain a stock award plan for both employees and for non-employee directors.  The plan provides for the", "bbox": [179.2, 164.1, 1110.3, 187.1]}, {"text": "grant of a variety of equity awards, including options (generally non-qualified options),  restricted stock, performance", "bbox": [123.0, 189.1, 1110.1, 212.1]}, {"text": "shares, and restricted stock units (\"RSUs\") to key employees (as determined by the Compensation and Management", "bbox": [123.0, 214.1, 1094.5, 237.1]}, {"text": "Development Committee of the Board of Directors) for periods not exceeding ten years.  Options granted to employees", "bbox": [123.0, 239.1, 1122.8, 262.1]}, {"text": "generally vest incrementally over four years.  Restricted stock generally cliff vests after three years.  Performance shares", "bbox": [123.0, 264.1, 1133.3, 287.2]}, {"text": "vest upon attainment of the stated performance targets and minimum service requirements and are converted into shares of", "bbox": [123.0, 289.1, 1150.7, 312.2]}, {"text": "common stock upon distribution.  RSUs represent the right to receive an equal number of shares of common stock and are", "bbox": [123.0, 314.1, 1146.6, 337.2]}, {"text": "converted into shares of common stock upon distribution.  As of December 31, 2013, there were 22.0 million shares that", "bbox": [123.0, 339.1, 1131.3, 362.2]}, {"text": "remained available for grant under the plan.", "bbox": [123.0, 364.1, 488.3, 387.2]}, {"text": "Non-employee directors are entitled to an annual distribution of stock options, common stock, or restricted stock", "bbox": [179.2, 414.1, 1124.2, 437.2]}, {"tex